OL,3,CGang jailed for killing father in
OL,4,Cbaseball bat and knife attack
OL,6,FSix men have been jailed over a fatal
OL,7,Fattack on a man in a park in Dewsbury.
OL,9,FShamus Hussain, 39, was followed and
OL,10,Fattacked in broad daylight, by men
OL,11,Farmed with baseball bats and hockey
OL,12,Fsticks on July 12, 2025.
OL,14,FHe died after being stabbed in the
OL,15,Fback.
OL,17,FSaqlain Ali, 22, Basit Ali, 32, Sakeb
OL,18,FAli Khan, 33, and Zeeshan Khan, 19,
OL,19,Fwere all found guilty of murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
