OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779196277
OL,3,CGang jailed for killing father in
OL,4,Cbaseball bat and knife attack
OL,6,FSaqlain Ali was sentenced to life with
OL,7,Fa minimum of 21 years, 56 days.
OL,9,FBasit Ali and Sakeb Ali Khan were both
OL,10,Fsentenced to life with a minimum of 15
OL,11,Fyears, 56 days.
OL,13,FZeeshan Khan was sentenced to life
OL,14,Fwith a minimum of ten years and 64
OL,15,Fdays.
OL,17,FAsim Akram, 21, and Faizaan Akram, 19,
OL,18,Fwere found guilty of manslaughter.
OL,19,FThey were both sentenced to seven
OL,20,Fyears in prison.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
