OL,3,CGang jailed for killing father in
OL,4,Cbaseball bat and knife attack
OL,6,FLeeds Crown Court heard the incident
OL,7,Fhappened after a verbal argument
OL,8,Fbetween Shamus, Basit Ali, Sakeb Ali
OL,9,FKhan, Zeeshan Khan and another man on
OL,10,FPilgrim Drive. Mr Hussain was then
OL,11,Ffollowed into Crow Nest Park.
OL,13,FCCTV footage captured the attack,
OL,14,Fshowing the men running towards Mr.
OL,15,FHussain.
OL,17,FPaying tribute to Mr. Hussain from
OL,18,FDewsbury Moor, his family said: "As a
OL,19,Ffamily we have been left heartbroken
OL,20,Fby the death of Shamus.
OL,26,@zD@aOU
