OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779196277
OL,3,CGang jailed for killing father in
OL,4,Cbaseball bat and knife attack
OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentencing, Det Ch
OL,7,FInsp James Entwistle, the senior
OL,8,Finvestigating officer, said: "Last
OL,9,Fsummer, Shamus Hussain was assaulted
OL,10,Fin a Dewsbury park in broad daylight.
OL,11,FThe attack was both violent and
OL,12,Fentirely senseless, leaving him with
OL,13,Finjuries from which he tragically died.
OL,15,F"Our thoughts remain with Shamus'
OL,16,Floved ones who had to endure a lengthy
OL,17,Ftrial before seeing his killers
OL,18,Fbrought to justice. Nothing can undo
OL,19,Fthe loss they have suffered, but I
OL,20,Fhope today's sentences will bring them
OL,21,Fsome comfort."
OL,26,@pD@^OUwD@AOU
